Get up

740
01:30:53,561 --> 01:30:57,554
Yes! This is the face!

741
01:30:59,167 --> 01:31:00,498
"Mr Padamsee...
- Yes, sir?"

742
01:31:00,602 --> 01:31:03,503
She's here for the audition.
Talk to her.

743
01:31:06,775 --> 01:31:09,608
Lucky girl!
- May I know what's it all about?

744
01:31:09,778 --> 01:31:13,111
"Sure, I'll explain.
And you are?"

745
01:31:13,281 --> 01:31:16,773
"Rahul. Rahul Roy, sir.
And this is Anu Varghese."

746
01:31:17,118 --> 01:31:20,519
Nice to meet you both.
And that was Mr Paul.

747
01:31:21,122 --> 01:31:25,115
He's here from Paris to
choose Indian models...

748
01:31:25,226 --> 01:31:30,129
"and he thinks you can take part
in the competition, if you wish to"

749
01:31:30,465 --> 01:31:34,128
But I... I was here
looking for a typist's job.

750
01:31:35,537 --> 01:31:40,531
"Typist? You don't know. If you're
chosen, you'll go places"

751
01:31:40,809 --> 01:31:44,142
The sky is the limit!
- But I...

752
01:31:45,547 --> 01:31:48,311
There's no time to think.
The audition takes place next week.

753
01:31:49,150 --> 01:31:52,142
"Thank you, Mr Padamsee.
Anu will surely participate."

754
