Wow! What a gait!
She's too much!

755
01:32:15,689 --> 01:32:19,955
Shut up! That's no dress...
she looks like a witch!

756
01:32:30,471 --> 01:32:36,467
"And look at her, Master! Wow!
- Stop barking like a dog!"

757
01:32:37,978 --> 01:32:42,472
Wait for Anu... she's going to
knock them all over! All of them!

758
01:33:25,292 --> 01:33:26,953
Thank you.

759
01:33:31,698 --> 01:33:37,967
"As we all know, we're all here
to choose an Indian model..."

760
01:33:38,305 --> 01:33:41,468
for Paris's Jean Cardin.

761
01:33:42,643 --> 01:33:45,976
There's a special announcement.
On behalf of Jean Cardin...

762
01:33:46,313 --> 01:33:49,646
