And also a free tour of Europe!

764
01:33:57,424 --> 01:33:59,654
"So get a hold on your hearts,
friends."

765
01:33:59,927 --> 01:34:04,261
The model we have chosen
today is...

766
01:34:05,432 --> 01:34:06,922
Miss...

767
01:34:08,001 --> 01:34:10,435
Miss Anu Varghese

768
01:34:27,287 --> 01:34:29,278
Congratulations.

769
01:34:46,974 --> 01:34:51,468
I had heard a story as a child.
That of the Prince of Dreams...

770
01:34:52,980 --> 01:34:58,919
who took the hand of an ugly orphan
and turned her into a beautiful fairy.

771
01:35:00,420 --> 01:35:05,915
Some stories turn out to be true.
Atleast in my case.

772
01:35:09,429 --> 01:35:13,661
The one who gave me a sense of
belonging and made me feel wanted...

773
01:35:13,767 --> 01:35:15,758
was Rahul.

774
01:35:17,938 --> 01:35:20,930
"Rahul, please come here."

775
01:35:23,944 --> 01:35:25,935
And take my hand before this crowd.

776
01:36:01,982 --> 01:36:07,921
My heart beats for you

777
01:36:15,429 --> 01:36:17,420
It beats for you

778
01:36:20,667 --> 01:36:26,663
"The sight of you makes
my heart skip a beat"

779
01:36:34,281 --> 01:36:36,272
It skips a beat

780
