784
01:37:33,373 --> 01:37:38,436
"Press it in your arms,
this fair-skinned body"

785
01:37:38,945 --> 01:37:43,678
"How else will I quench
this fire within?"

786
01:37:44,951 --> 01:37:50,947
A fire rages in my heart

