791
01:38:57,390 --> 01:39:02,225
"It's a realisation that
you have come of age"

792
01:39:03,230 --> 01:39:08,395
Love intoxicates me

793
01:39:08,902 --> 01:39:13,635
"It's fun, my love"

794
01:39:14,908 --> 01:39:20,904
"I can't control my heart,
no matter how much I try"

795
01:39:28,655 --> 01:39:30,646
I can't control it

796
01:39:33,660 --> 01:39:39,656
My heart beats for you

797
01:39:47,274 --> 01:39:49,674
It beats for you

798
01:40:05,225 --> 01:40:10,891
"Anu, I can't control myself anymore.
Let's get married."

799
01:40:13,233 --> 01:40:15,224
Anytime you wish to.

800
01:40:19,239 --> 01:40:21,230
"I love you, Anu."

801
01:40:34,988 --> 01:40:37,252
You're better than
I was told you are.

802
01:40:38,258 --> 01:40:41,659
What?
- I'm Rahul's mother.

803
01:40:48,602 --> 01:40:50,593
Please come in.

804
01:40:53,873 --> 01:40:58,367
"It's a good thing to achieve so much
at such a young age, my child."

805
01:40:59,212 --> 01:41:02,875
"In fact, it's necessary for women
to stand on their own feet."

806
01:41:05,218 --> 01:41:07,618
"What would I have done,
if I didn't have a job?"

807
01:41:11,224 --> 01:41:13,215
"Don't ever stop working, dear."

808
01:41:14,894 --> 01:41:19,228
"What will you have? Tea or coffee?
- Nothing, Anu. Sit down."

809
01:41:26,906 --> 01:41:29,898
"It's like this, Anu.
I'm Rahul's mother."

810
01:41:31,411 --> 01:41:33,402
I wouldn't wish the two
of you anything bad.

811
01:41:35,248 --> 01:41:39,912
But the haste the two of you
are showing you to get married...

812
01:41:41,254 --> 01:41:47,250
is bad for your love
and for your future.

813
01:41:47,594 --> 01:41:49,585
I don't understand.

814
01:41:51,765 --> 01:41:57,431
Have you ever wondered why Rahul
never brought you to meet me?

815
01:41:58,938 --> 01:42:01,270
"Well...
- Look, Anu."

816
01:42:01,941 --> 01:42:05,672
"Rahul can lie to the whole world,
even to himself..."

817
01:42:06,279 --> 01:42:08,270
but he can't tell lies to me.

818
01:42:08,448 --> 01:42:10,780
He knows he has not achieved
anything till now.

819
01:42:11,951 --> 01:42:13,282
He also realises that...

820
01:42:13,453 --> 01:42:16,786
there's suddenly a distance between
the two of you.

821
01:42:17,957 --> 01:42:20,949
"Anu, you make much
more money than he does."

822
01:42:22,529 --> 01:42:25,965
"You have a name in society,
an identity of your own."

823
01:42:27,300 --> 01:42:32,294
But Rahul is looked at
as only your boyfriend.

824
01:42:33,306 --> 01:42:35,706
The fiance of a successful model.

825
01:42:36,309 --> 01:42:38,470
"Mother...
- It sounds bitter, my dear."

826
01:42:39,713 --> 01:42:45,481
But it's true. And if you want
to change things...

827
01:42:46,319 --> 01:42:51,313
give Rahul some time.
I know he has the talent...

828
01:42:51,491 --> 01:42:53,425
and ability to achieve something.

829
01:42:53,760 --> 01:42:56,752
"Rahul will pressurise you
to get married, Anu."

830
01:42:57,764 --> 01:42:59,755
"Because now that
you are a success..."

831
01:43:00,667 --> 01:43:03,431
the fear of losing you
haunts him all the time.

832
01:43:05,438 --> 01:43:07,429
"I'll tell you something
out of experience, my dear."

833
01:43:08,274 --> 01:43:13,268
A relationship succeeds only when
the people involved are equals.

834
01:43:16,683 --> 01:43:20,949
That's it then.
This is all I wanted to say.

835
01:43:22,956 --> 01:43:26,289
And don't tell Rahul that we
have talked about these things.

836
01:43:27,460 --> 01:43:29,451
He won't be able to understand.

837
01:43:39,706 --> 01:43:42,470
"Okay, Rahul. Say hi to Anu
on my behalf."

838
01:43:42,709 --> 01:43:44,301
Okay.
- Bye.

839
01:43:44,477 --> 01:43:46,468
"One moment, Pallo."

840
01:43:47,714 --> 01:43:49,978
Give me a hundred rupees.
- Sure.

841
01:43:50,483 --> 01:43:53,919
I'll have to take a cab
to drop Anu home.

842
01:43:55,922 --> 01:43:59,756
"I now owe you 26,535 rupees, okay?"

843
01:44:00,426 --> 01:44:03,259
"I told you, Rahul. There are
no accounts between friends."

844
01:44:03,363 --> 01:44:05,763
"You can have more, if you wish.
- No, this is enough."

845
01:44:07,267 --> 01:44:09,428
Anu's a big model now.

846
01:44:10,270 --> 01:44:13,671
I don't like to take her out
in crowded buses and trains.

847
01:44:15,275 --> 01:44:17,266
I'd rather take money from you.

848
01:44:17,377 --> 01:44:23,941
But I can't take advantage of the
success my future wife has made.

849
01:44:24,684 --> 01:44:27,778
"I understand. Okay...
- Thanks, buddy."

850
01:44:28,288 --> 01:44:29,778
Bye.
- See you.

851
01:44:30,390 --> 01:44:33,450
"Anu, turn this side... turn left.
More life!"

852
01:44:35,295 --> 01:44:37,456
Vibrant! Yes!

853
01:44:38,298 --> 01:44:40,698
Excuse me... whom do you
wish to meet?

854
01:44:41,301 --> 01:44:43,701
I'm here to meet Anu.
- You can't meet her right now.

855
01:44:43,970 --> 01:44:46,302
You can ask if you wish...
- She's busy right now.

856
01:44:46,706 --> 01:44:48,697
Please go out. Please.

857
01:44:51,311 --> 01:44:53,302
"Salil, he's with me."

858
01:44:53,413 --> 01:44:57,907
"Salil, you stupid donkey!
Don't you know how to talk to people?"

859
01:44:58,418 --> 01:45:00,409
Come and sit down here!

860
01:45:00,920 --> 01:45:03,650
"Sorry, Rahul. Really sorry.
- It's all right."

861
01:45:08,661 --> 01:45:10,652
Wait... wait.

862
01:45:12,665 --> 01:45:16,260
"Take your hand up, please.
Yes, that's it."

863
01:45:19,672 --> 01:45:21,264
That's it.

864
01:45:22,275 --> 01:45:24,266
"It's okay, thank you.
I'll do it."

865
01:45:27,280 --> 01:45:30,943
That's it... a close-up.
Come on.

866
01:45:33,953 --> 01:45:35,944
Okay. Hold on.

867
01:45:36,689 --> 01:45:39,954
"Anu, get into the swimming costume.
- What?"

868
01:45:40,293 --> 01:45:42,022
Hurry up.
- Swimming costume?

869
01:45:42,462 --> 01:45:44,453
Anu's not wearing
that swimming costume.

870
01:45:48,301 --> 01:45:51,964
Hello! Who asked you?

871
01:45:52,705 --> 01:45:54,639
Don't disturb us.
Let us get on with our work.

872
01:45:55,408 --> 01:45:57,239
"Okay, get on with your work."

873
01:45:57,410 --> 01:46:00,243
"But Anu's not wearing that
swimming costume, I said."

874
01:46:01,247 --> 01:46:05,650
"Mr Padamsee, what's going on?
I say, what's going on?"

875
01:46:06,252 --> 01:46:12,248
"Rahul, come on... it's all right.
Take it easy, Rahul."

876
01:46:12,659 --> 01:46:16,254
"Come, let's have some coffee.
- No."

877
01:46:16,930 --> 01:46:19,421
"Anu, you will not
wear those clothes."

878
01:46:20,667 --> 01:46:22,259
Hold it!

879
01:46:22,435 --> 01:46:24,426
Who the hell are you
to tell us that?

880
01:46:24,938 --> 01:46:28,669
"Anu, tell them who I am."

881
01:46:29,442 --> 01:46:32,434
"Okay, if you won't tell them,
I will."

882
01:46:33,279 --> 01:46:36,680
I'm Anu's fiance. We're going
to get married very soon.

883
01:46:36,950 --> 01:46:39,282
"I don't understand what
he's saying, Anu."

884
01:46:39,686 --> 01:46:42,678
Haven't you told him?
According to our contract with you...

885
01:46:42,789 --> 01:46:46,452
"you can't marry for another 2 years.
- But, sir..."

886
01:46:46,693 --> 01:46:48,684
Salil! Get that
file of the contract.

887
01:46:50,296 --> 01:46:52,287
Hurry up.

888
01:46:54,400 --> 01:46:57,392
Is it true that you've signed
a contract like that?

889
01:46:57,904 --> 01:46:59,394
Without even telling me?

890
01:46:59,639 --> 01:47:01,903
"And I've been dreaming of marriage,
like a fool!"

891
01:47:02,642 --> 01:47:05,406
"I've been busy making arrangements!
- Please calm down, Rahul."

892
01:47:05,912 --> 01:47:09,404
I'll explain everything later.
- Not later!

893
01:47:09,515 --> 01:47:12,643
Tell me right now!
What's happening here?

894
01:47:13,252 --> 01:47:15,243
Why have you done this?

895
01:47:23,930 --> 01:47:28,663
"Rahul, you know how important it is
for me to achieve something in life."

896
01:47:30,269 --> 01:47:34,262
"To achieve that,
I had to sign this contract."

897
01:47:34,440 --> 01:47:39,275
"All right, so break this contract.
Just leave them! Come with me, Anu."

898
01:47:39,445 --> 01:47:41,436
"It isn't so easy to break
a contract, Rahul."

899
01:47:41,681 --> 01:47:45,674
"I'm talking to Anu, not you!
Don't interrupt!"

900
01:47:47,787 --> 01:47:54,215
"Let's go, Anu. Come on.
- No, Rahul. I can't do that."

901
01:47:59,632 --> 01:48:02,226
"All right, I understand."

902
01:48:04,237 --> 01:48:07,638
I understand everything.

903
01:48:22,655 --> 01:48:25,647
"Don't worry, Anu.
You've done the right thing."

904
01:48:26,659 --> 01:48:30,925
This is in your interest and ours.
- You won't understand.

905
01:48:34,267 --> 01:48:36,667
"I didn't do this for myself,
nor for the contract."

906
01:48:39,939 --> 01:48:43,670
I've done all this only for Rahul.

907
01:48:45,945 --> 01:48:47,936
Only for him.

908
01:49:40,766 --> 01:49:44,668
"Anu, I will meet you only when
I get to be something in life"

909
01:49:45,671 --> 01:49:50,438
"If I don't make it big...
do forget me. Forever."

910
01:49:51,277 --> 01:49:52,437
- Rahul

911
01:50:18,404 --> 01:50:21,237
Without you...

912
01:50:22,408 --> 01:50:24,399
I will live

913
01:50:26,245 --> 01:50:31,410
"I will swallow the poison
that my life is"

914
01:50:32,585 --> 01:50:38,922
"It doesn't matter
if I'm heart-broken"

915
01:50:40,259 --> 01:50:45,925
"It doesn't matter
if I'm heart-broken"

916
01:50:49,268 --> 01:50:51,668
Without you...

917
01:50:53,272 --> 01:50:55,365
I will live

918
01:50:56,609 --> 01:51:02,377
"I will swallow the poison
that my life is"

919
01:51:04,217 --> 01:51:06,208
"That's wonderful, young man!"

920
01:51:06,552 --> 01:51:12,616
Your voice has the feeling and
pain I have been looking for.

921
01:51:13,960 --> 01:51:21,389
At last! You have been introduced
to love and pain.

922
01:51:22,401 --> 01:51:24,892
Want to know who I am?

923
01:51:26,239 --> 01:51:29,231
I'm Bashir Khan.

924
01:51:29,642 --> 01:51:32,406
"On behalf of Super Cassettes
Industries, it's my duty..."

925
01:51:32,645 --> 01:51:34,636
to show new artists
the way to stardom.

926
01:51:35,248 --> 01:51:40,242
Come with me and I will take you
to the place you deserve.

927
01:51:40,653 --> 01:51:42,245
Come on.

928
01:51:47,260 --> 01:51:53,665
What has your love given me?

929
01:51:54,433 --> 01:52:00,929
"I loved you and
you were unfaithful"

930
01:52:02,008 --> 01:52:08,675
"It was my mistake...
what did I seek?"

931
01:52:09,282 --> 01:52:15,687
"I expected love
from an unfaithful girl"

932
01:52:15,955 --> 01:52:19,288
"How will you know
what pining is?"

933
01:52:20,393 --> 01:52:22,953
You are selfish and insensitive

934
01:52:23,963 --> 01:52:26,693
"Go away, heartless girl..."

935
01:52:27,466 --> 01:52:30,299
I have seen your love

936
01:52:31,370 --> 01:52:34,965
"I now know what you are,
O merciless one"

937
01:52:38,477 --> 01:52:40,968
Without you...

938
01:52:42,481 --> 01:52:44,711
I will live

939
01:52:46,319 --> 01:52:51,723
"I will swallow the poison
that my life is"

940
01:52:55,995 --> 01:52:59,431
"How are you, Rahul? Speak up...
haven't heard you for so many days."

941
01:52:59,765 --> 01:53:01,926
What will I say?
- Say anything.

942
01:53:02,435 --> 01:53:04,665
Is someone else listening
to my voice too?

943
01:53:05,004 --> 01:53:09,668
What? Oh no.
I'm all alone.

944
01:53:10,276 --> 01:53:14,940
"Listen, Pallo.
I've known you for years."

945
01:53:15,681 --> 01:53:17,945
I don't want anyone to
listen to my voice...

946
01:53:18,451 --> 01:53:21,284
nor do I want to listen
to anyone. That's it.

947
01:53:21,687 --> 01:53:27,956
"Little did I know that my beloved
would break the promises of love"

948
01:53:28,694 --> 01:53:35,293
"If only I knew what
you had on your mind"

949
01:53:36,469 --> 01:53:42,965
"I loved you so much.
I gave you my heart"

950
01:53:43,576 --> 01:53:49,981
"I was so naive,
I couldn't understand anything"

951
01:53:50,483 --> 01:53:53,418
I wept

952
01:53:54,520 --> 01:53:56,920
Tears flowed from my eyes

953
01:53:57,923 --> 01:54:00,653
My shattered heart...

954
01:54:01,427 --> 01:54:04,260
is a sign of your love

955
01:54:04,930 --> 01:54:09,424
"How will I ever forget
how unfaithful you were?"

956
01:54:12,938 --> 01:54:14,929
Without you...

957
01:54:16,675 --> 01:54:18,666
I will live

958
01:54:20,279 --> 01:54:25,945
"I will swallow the poison
that my life is"

959
01:54:27,620 --> 01:54:32,956
"It doesn't matter
if I'm heart-broken"

960
01:54:34,693 --> 01:54:40,290
"It doesn't matter
if I'm heart-broken"

961
01:54:43,903 --> 01:54:46,303
Without you...

962
01:54:47,973 --> 01:54:49,964
I will live

963
01:54:51,310 --> 01:54:56,646
"I will swallow the poison
that my life is"

964
01:54:58,918 --> 01:55:00,909
I will live...

965
01:55:02,755 --> 01:55:04,916
I will live...

966
01:55:06,425 --> 01:55:08,655
I will live...

967
01:55:17,870 --> 01:55:22,273
"Oh my God! I'm really sorry
I kept you waiting, Anu."

968
01:55:22,675 --> 01:55:24,666
"Two minutes more, okay?"

969
01:55:27,446 --> 01:55:30,438
Two minutes?
What do you mean?

970
01:55:31,684 --> 01:55:36,951
You've got to finalise artworks
of four of my music albums today.

971
01:55:37,356 --> 01:55:41,952
"Relax, just relax. Why do you get
serious with such things?"

972
01:55:42,461 --> 01:55:47,455
Atleast give me the pictures of
the singers and the other details.

973
01:55:47,700 --> 01:55:49,292
Here.

974
01:55:53,639 --> 01:55:56,403
"What do I see, Mr Bashir?
- What?"

975
01:55:57,409 --> 01:56:01,903
Rahul Roy? Are you releasing
a record by him?

976
01:56:02,915 --> 01:56:05,907
"Yes. So what?
- Come on, Mr Bashir."

977
01:56:06,418 --> 01:56:09,910
Why're you encouraging
this two-penny singer?

978
01:56:10,656 --> 01:56:15,423
"As your marketing advisor,
it's my duty to advise you..."

979
01:56:15,528 --> 01:56:21,660
not to make such mistakes. It could
be damaging for your company's image.

980
01:56:24,770 --> 01:56:27,261
"Mr Padamsee, please step out.
- One minute."

981
01:56:27,940 --> 01:56:32,434
"I said, come with me.
I want to talk to you."

982
01:56:41,954 --> 01:56:43,945
What happened?

983
01:56:44,957 --> 01:56:48,290
A petty man shows
his pettiness...

984
01:56:48,961 --> 01:56:51,691
when he unnecessarily casts
aspersions on someone's capabilities.

985
01:56:51,964 --> 01:56:53,295
What?

986
01:56:54,400 --> 01:56:59,633
"I know why you hate Rahul.
- Yes, I hate Rahul."

987
01:57:00,239 --> 01:57:04,403
What's this lifetime? I don't
spare my enemies in any lifetime.

988
01:57:04,643 --> 01:57:10,240
"When I'm around, not you, not the
whole world can do any harm to Rahul."

989
01:57:12,251 --> 01:57:16,915
"Mr Padamsee, if you try to
sabotage Rahul's album..."

990
01:57:18,424 --> 01:57:20,654
I'll break your contract
and walk out.

991
01:57:21,927 --> 01:57:25,260
"Don't threaten me, Anu.
Don't."

992
01:57:28,767 --> 01:57:30,257
What are you doing?

993
01:57:30,369 --> 01:57:32,428
"You have invested a lot
in my face, haven't you?"

994
01:57:34,940 --> 01:57:38,273
You will have to release
Rahul's album.

995
01:57:40,279 --> 01:57:44,682
"Or else, I'll burn my face.
- No! No!"

996
01:57:44,950 --> 01:57:47,680
Go on.
- I'm going... don't do it!

997
01:58:01,233 --> 01:58:03,895
"Excuse me, sir.
May I come in?"

998
01:58:05,237 --> 01:58:08,638
"Welcome, Rahul Roy!
I've been thinking about you."

999
01:58:08,741 --> 01:58:11,232
Where have you been?
I just didn't see you around.

1000
01:58:11,410 --> 01:58:14,402
"I've been around, sir.
- What can I do for you?"

1001
01:58:14,647 --> 01:58:18,413
"I need some money, sir.
If I could have it?"

1002
01:58:18,917 --> 01:58:20,908
Some money?
- Yes.

1003
01:58:21,253 --> 01:58:23,244
If I could have a 1000 rupees.

1004
01:58:23,422 --> 01:58:28,655
"Is that all? Don't you know then?
- Know what, sir?"

1005
01:58:28,927 --> 01:58:34,263
"Look, we're getting reports from
our agents across the country."

1006
01:58:34,433 --> 01:58:37,664
Your song is a super-hit young man!
It's a super-hit.

1007
01:58:38,003 --> 01:58:43,669
"The chairman is going to give you a
gold disc and a cheque for 200,000!"

1008
01:58:44,443 --> 01:58:46,934
"Talk in terms of hundreds
of thousands, my friend."

1009
01:58:47,279 --> 01:58:49,941
Not mere thousands!

1010
01:59:06,231 --> 01:59:08,222
Hello?
- Hello.

1011
01:59:08,400 --> 01:59:10,391
"Have you received the flowers, Anu?"

1012
01:59:11,470 --> 01:59:15,634
"Know what I'm celebrating?
I'm a star, Anu. I've become a star!"

1013
01:59:16,909 --> 01:59:21,243
"This evening, I'm getting a cheque
of 200,000 and a trophy."

1014
01:59:22,247 --> 01:59:24,647
"I've telephoned my mother,
Pallo and Master."

1015
01:59:24,917 --> 01:59:26,908
They'll meet me at the function.

1016
01:59:27,920 --> 01:59:31,913
"As I promised, I'm coming over, Anu.
I'll have lunch with you."

1017
01:59:32,257 --> 01:59:34,418
"And we'll both leave for
the function, okay?"

1018
01:59:36,595 --> 01:59:38,654
"I love you, Anu. I love you."

1019
01:59:39,431 --> 01:59:42,662
I love you Rahul. I love you.

1020
01:59:50,776 --> 01:59:54,371
Like you need to breathe...

1021
01:59:55,214 --> 02:00:01,380
like you need to breathe to live...

1022
02:00:02,221 --> 02:00:08,217
"you need a beloved
to love"

1023
02:00:11,230 --> 02:00:14,393
Like you need a lamp...

1024
02:00:15,901 --> 02:00:21,635
"like you need a lamp
for light..."

1025
02:00:22,407 --> 02:00:28,642
"you need a beloved
to fall in love with"

1026
02:00:31,650 --> 02:00:37,646
You need a beloved to love

1027
02:00:42,261 --> 02:00:43,660
Hi!

1028
02:00:44,930 --> 02:00:46,659
Surprised?

1029
02:00:46,932 --> 02:00:52,427
Maybe you are surprised
to see me here. Right?

1030
02:00:53,705 --> 02:00:55,195
No?

1031
02:00:57,376 --> 02:01:02,211
"In fact, I wanted to surprise you.
So I landed here like this."

1032
02:01:02,381 --> 02:01:05,873
Know what the surprise is?
- No.

1033
02:01:06,218 --> 02:01:10,382
"It is something like this. Anyway,
what's the point in harassing you?"

1034
02:01:14,393 --> 02:01:16,384
You're going to Paris!

1035
02:01:16,628 --> 02:01:20,621
This is a small gift from me.
Please...

1036
02:01:28,640 --> 02:01:31,404
So you've already heard
about going to Paris?

1037
02:01:32,244 --> 02:01:35,407
I'm late. No problem.
It's all right.

1038
02:01:37,649 --> 02:01:41,415
"Sorry, sir. You must leave now.
I'm expecting someone."

1039
02:01:43,255 --> 02:01:45,246
These flowers are to celebrate
Rahul's success.

1040
02:01:45,657 --> 02:01:48,421
He's coming over for lunch.
- So I've come at the wrong time?

1041
02:01:49,361 --> 02:01:53,263
"Now listen to me. In 15 days,
you're going with me to Paris."

1042
02:01:53,432 --> 02:01:56,924
Although I don't want to interfere
with your personal life...

1043
02:01:57,436 --> 02:02:01,668
I must tell you something.
The less you see of Rahul...

1044
02:02:02,274 --> 02:02:04,765
the better it will be
for your career.

1045
02:02:05,444 --> 02:02:10,939
"From today, Rahul is my life and
my career. I'm in love with him..."

1046
02:02:11,950 --> 02:02:14,680
and we're going to get married
very soon.

1047
02:02:14,953 --> 02:02:20,687
No! You know very well Anu that you
can't marry for another 2 years.

1048
02:02:20,959 --> 02:02:25,293
You have signed a contract with me.
If you try to break the contract...

1049
02:02:25,697 --> 02:02:29,963
"it'll be very bad for you.
- Do what you want to do, Padamsee."

1050
02:02:30,702 --> 02:02:32,966
I don't care.

1051
02:02:34,973 --> 02:02:39,467
Rahul has become a very big singer.
He'll fight you in the courts.

1052
02:02:41,713 --> 02:02:43,704
"I'm not one of those
who take defeat, Anu."

1053
02:02:44,316 --> 02:02:46,307
I'll be too much to handle
for the two of you.

1054
02:02:47,486 --> 02:02:49,477
Remember that.

1055
02:02:50,722 --> 02:02:52,713
Mr Padamsee...

1056
02:02:56,428 --> 02:03:00,421
take this as you go.
There's no room for this either.

1057
02:03:05,671 --> 02:03:07,662
Never mind.

1058
02:03:24,289 --> 02:03:26,951
"Hello, Mr Rahul Roy.
Congratulations!"

1059
02:03:30,295 --> 02:03:36,461
But I wonder if I must congratulate
you or your fiancee.

1060
02:03:37,302 --> 02:03:40,294
"I'm talking about Anu.
- It's one and the same thing, sir."

1061
02:03:40,706 --> 02:03:46,975
"Oh yes. Behind every successful man,
there is a woman."

1062
02:03:47,079 --> 02:03:49,309
And this adage you have proved
to be true today.

1063
02:03:49,648 --> 02:03:51,980
"What do you mean?
- Come on, Rahul."

1064
02:03:52,317 --> 02:03:56,913
Don't pretend not to know.
You aren't so innocent.

1065
02:03:58,256 --> 02:04:01,419
"Come to the point, Mr Padamsee.
What are you getting at?"

1066
02:04:01,660 --> 02:04:07,656
Just that you used Anu very well
to scale the ladder of success.

1067
02:04:08,667 --> 02:04:13,263
I must compliment you for that.
Had Anu not forced me...

1068
02:04:13,438 --> 02:04:16,430
your album would never have
been released and you...

1069
02:04:16,675 --> 02:04:19,269
"you'd have been rotting in that
restaurant, still singing there."

1070
02:04:19,678 --> 02:04:21,669
You must thank Anu.

1071
02:04:22,280 --> 02:04:24,942
It's because of her that
you are worth something today.

1072
02:04:26,284 --> 02:04:31,449
No. I don't believe this.
It's a lie.

1073
02:04:32,290 --> 02:04:35,691
"Lies are shortlived, Rahul.
And since this is the truth..."

1074
02:04:36,294 --> 02:04:39,286
it'll be out before the world soon.
By then maybe...

1075
02:04:39,698 --> 02:04:43,293
you'll be used to a life
that is dependent on women.

1076
02:04:43,702 --> 02:04:46,296
Stop it!
- Why're you angry with me?

1077
02:04:46,705 --> 02:04:49,697
"If you don't like what I say,
go and be angry with Anu."

1078
02:04:50,308 --> 02:04:53,903
Go and ask her why she has
given your success a stigma.

1079
02:04:54,413 --> 02:05:00,648
"Grab her collar, not mine. Okay?
You claim to be a real man..."

1080
02:05:00,919 --> 02:05:03,410
"spurn the charity she gave you,
if you have the guts."

1081
02:05:04,256 --> 02:05:06,247
Kick the success. Go on.

1082
02:05:42,461 --> 02:05:44,452
Where had you gone away?

1083
02:05:47,699 --> 02:05:50,293
Don't leave me and
go away ever again.

1084
02:05:56,241 --> 02:05:59,642
"Rahul, you're hurting me!"

1085
02:06:02,647 --> 02:06:06,640
What did you get out of
humiliating me? What?

1086
02:06:07,252 --> 02:06:09,914
"What kind of a joke is this, Rahul?"

1087
02:06:10,655 --> 02:06:12,919
That's exactly what I want to know.
Why did you play a joke on me?

1088
02:06:14,259 --> 02:06:17,660
"Why did you do it? Why?
- What's gotten into you, Rahul?"

1089
02:06:19,264 --> 02:06:22,256
What do you want to say?
- Stop it! Stop it!

1090
02:06:23,869 --> 02:06:25,860
Padamsee has told me everything!

1091
02:06:26,271 --> 02:06:28,933
Your farce isn't working
with me anymore. Okay?

1092
02:06:30,275 --> 02:06:36,680
"Anu, you have belittled my pride
and my self-respect today."

1093
02:06:37,949 --> 02:06:40,679
You have poisoned my life forever!

1094
02:06:42,287 --> 02:06:44,687
And what did I ask you for? What?

1095
02:06:44,956 --> 02:06:47,686
Why did you have to do me
a favour in charity?

1096
02:06:49,961 --> 02:06:51,792
I can't believe it!

1097
02:06:51,963 --> 02:06:56,400
I'm beginning to hate you
and your face!

1098
02:06:57,235 --> 02:07:01,638
I hate you! I hate you!

1099
02:07:04,910 --> 02:07:09,643
"No! Stay right there!
And don't try to follow me, okay?"

1100
02:07:28,667 --> 02:07:30,658
What's up? Rahul hasn't yet arrived?

1101
02:07:30,936 --> 02:07:33,268
"Our chairman, Mr Gulshan Kumar
will be arriving any moment now."

1102
02:07:33,438 --> 02:07:35,668
"This is Rahul's mother, Mr Bashir.
- Hello."

1103
02:07:35,941 --> 02:07:38,671
He has gone to fetch a friend.
He'll be arriving any moment.

1104
02:07:38,777 --> 02:07:41,439
"Go and make a call, Pallo.
He must be on his way."

1105
02:07:51,957 --> 02:07:54,892
"Hello, sir.
Welcome Mr Gulshan Kumar."

1106
02:07:58,230 --> 02:08:00,630
Where could he have gone?
Is no one taking the call?

1107
02:08:00,899 --> 02:08:02,730
What are we to do now?

1108
02:08:02,901 --> 02:08:06,894
"This is the limit, Mrs Roy.
The Chairman has arrived already."

1109
02:08:07,405 --> 02:08:10,636
Rahul has really embarrassed me.
- I'm extremely sorry.

1110
02:08:10,742 --> 02:08:16,237
You tell us what we must do.
- I'll start the function...

1111
02:08:16,648 --> 02:08:19,412
you can receive the cheque
on behalf on Rahul.

1112
02:08:19,651 --> 02:08:21,642
Me?
- Yes.

1113
02:08:22,654 --> 02:08:24,645
I'll start the function.

1114
02:08:50,282 --> 02:08:51,442
Hello.

1115
02:08:51,683 --> 02:08:53,617
"Mr Padamsee, I've got to say
something important to you."

1116
02:08:55,387 --> 02:08:58,879
Well?
- I'm willing to leave for Paris.

1117
02:09:23,415 --> 02:09:27,408
"Is Rahul there?
This is his friend, Pallu."

1118
02:09:30,655 --> 02:09:35,922
Where have you been all night?
- In hell! What is it to you?

1119
02:09:43,935 --> 02:09:46,665
Out! Get out.

1120
02:09:47,672 --> 02:09:49,936
There's no place for you
in this house anymore.

1121
02:09:51,676 --> 02:09:55,373
You try to humiliate us?
You belittle us?

1122
02:09:57,615 --> 02:09:59,207
Here's your money.

1123
02:09:59,384 --> 02:10:03,218
Go and have fun. Do as you please.
Just go to hell.

1124
02:10:03,321 --> 02:10:05,312
Mother...
- You keep out of this!

1125
02:10:06,624 --> 02:10:10,617
Do you know why this boy
keeps twisting our arms?

1126
02:10:11,396 --> 02:10:15,890
It's because we love him very much.
We love him more than necessary.

1127
02:10:16,901 --> 02:10:18,892
This is what his father did too.

1128
02:10:19,237 --> 02:10:23,401
"But what happened? Did I die,
after he left me?"

1129
02:10:24,409 --> 02:10:29,244
"Rahul, however strong
a relationship is..."

1130
02:10:29,647 --> 02:10:32,241
life does not end with it.

1131
02:10:32,917 --> 02:10:35,647
Anu won't die without you.
- Enough!

1132
02:10:36,254 --> 02:10:38,415
"Don't utter that bitch's name
in my presence, mother!"

1133
02:10:38,923 --> 02:10:44,657
Don't you dare abuse her!
I'll pull out your tongue!

1134
02:10:45,663 --> 02:10:48,655
Do you know what she has
done for you?

1135
02:10:48,933 --> 02:10:53,267
"Yes, I know! Which is why
I feel like killing myself!"

1136
02:10:53,605 --> 02:10:56,369
You don't know anything. Nothing.

1137
02:10:58,209 --> 02:11:00,609
"Whatever Anu did,
was at my behest."

1138
02:11:01,379 --> 02:11:05,611
I told her not to marry you till you
had reached some position in life.

1139
02:11:06,384 --> 02:11:08,375
And she obeyed me.

1140
02:11:09,220 --> 02:11:13,213
"You thought she was unfaithful,
but she didn't tell you the truth."

1141
02:11:13,725 --> 02:11:15,215
How about what Padamsee told me?

1142
02:11:15,393 --> 02:11:19,386
Why did she do me a favour?
Why make me a success?

1143
02:11:19,898 --> 02:11:24,232
"Nobody does anybody a favour,
Rahul. Anu only helped..."

1144
02:11:24,335 --> 02:11:28,897
in taking your voice to the people.
It's people who made you a success.

1145
02:11:29,240 --> 02:11:32,641
It's the public. If you
didn't have the talent...

1146
02:11:32,744 --> 02:11:34,735
would you ever reach this stage?

1147
02:11:36,247 --> 02:11:38,408
You gave Anu so much of love.

1148
02:11:38,917 --> 02:11:42,648
"And when she tried to reciprocate,
it hurts your ego so much?"

1149
02:11:43,988 --> 02:11:47,651
"Anu's love is for real, my son.
Don't humiliate her."

1150
02:11:49,260 --> 02:11:52,252
"You don't find true love
very often in life, Rahul."

1151
02:11:52,664 --> 02:11:56,259
Go and stop her. She's going
away to Paris... stop her!

1152
02:11:56,434 --> 02:11:58,664
"Bring her home. Go on, Rahul"

1153
02:12:00,271 --> 02:12:05,937
"There is a wall between you
and Anu, Rahul. And it's you!"

1154
02:12:06,277 --> 02:12:09,269
It's your pride!
Do away with it...

1155
02:12:09,447 --> 02:12:11,677
or you will regret it.

1156
02:12:14,786 --> 02:12:18,688
I realise today why people
consider a mother to be God.

1157
02:12:19,958 --> 02:12:23,450
"I'm leaving, mother.
I'll bring Anu here."

1158
02:12:24,295 --> 02:12:25,455
"I'll bring her home, mother."

1159
02:12:30,301 --> 02:12:34,294
Passengers traveling by British
Airways flight 316 to Paris...

1160
02:12:36,808 --> 02:12:38,298
Out of the way!

1161
02:13:03,935 --> 02:13:05,766
Watch it...
- Shut up!

1162
02:13:35,466 --> 02:13:37,457
"Step on it, Pallo! Faster!"

1163
02:13:41,706 --> 02:13:43,298
Stop here!

1164
02:13:52,817 --> 02:13:54,751
Get out of our way!

1165
02:13:56,654 --> 02:13:58,246
Let's go!

1166
02:14:06,264 --> 02:14:08,255
"Rahul, where are you going?"

1167
02:14:21,279 --> 02:14:23,679
Get in! Hurry up!

1168
02:14:27,285 --> 02:14:31,688
They're taking my car away!
Stop them!

1169
02:14:35,960 --> 02:14:37,951
Did you see him?

1170
02:14:38,963 --> 02:14:40,294
"Let's go, Sawant. Hurry up."

1171
02:14:51,709 --> 02:14:53,404
The cops are after us.

1172
02:15:25,443 --> 02:15:26,671
Only two.

1173
02:15:55,740 --> 02:15:57,731
"Brakes, Pallo! The brakes!"

1174
02:16:09,253 --> 02:16:14,247
Passengers travelling by British
Airways flight 316 requested to...

1175
02:16:14,659 --> 02:16:16,251
Come on!

1176
02:16:19,664 --> 02:16:21,928
You? What the hell
is all this?

1177
02:16:22,266 --> 02:16:24,928
"I'll explain, sir. But it's necessary
for me to reach the airport."

1178
02:16:25,269 --> 02:16:27,430
Or the girl will go away.
- That girl from the love story?

1179
02:16:27,538 --> 02:16:30,439
"Yes, sir! Please do something, sir!
- Please, sir."

1180
02:16:31,275 --> 02:16:32,936
"Hurry up, sir."

1181
02:16:36,681 --> 02:16:39,673
"Inspector, drive faster!
- Only 5 minutes to go!"

1182
02:16:47,458 --> 02:16:51,292
The last and final call for passengers
travelling by British Airways...

1183
02:16:51,395 --> 02:16:53,625
"flight 316 to Paris.
- Let's go, Anu."

1184
02:16:54,899 --> 02:16:56,890
Proceed for security check.
- Come on.

1185
02:17:09,247 --> 02:17:10,646
The airport.

1186
